pageProduct.name: Wanderlust Fully Charged 30 Capsules
pageProduct.description:
General Information

Used in Traditional Chinese Medicine to boost energy levels and in Western Herbal Medicine to increase mental alertness.

Wanderlust Fully Charged is a consciously created blend of plant actives. Korean Ginseng is used in Traditional Chinese Medicine to boost energy levels and strengthen Qi. Kola Nut is traditionally used in Western Herbal Medicine to improve mental alertness, decrease cognitive fatigue and enhance wakefulness. Green Tea is a natural source of caffeine.

Size: 30 Capsules

Warnings

Contains sulfites.

Adults only.

Contains 16 mg total caffeine per capsule. A cup of instant coffee contains approximately 80 mg of caffeine.

Caffeine intake more than 200 mg per day is not recommended during pregnancy or breastfeeding.

Talk to a TCM practitioner/health professional if you are unsure if this medicine is right for you.

If symptoms persist, talk to your health professional.

Ingredients

EACH CAPSULE CONTAINS:

Panax ginseng (Korean Ginseng) root ext. dry conc. 30 mg
Derived from fresh 1.5 g

Cola nitida (Kola Nut) fruit ext. dry conc. stand. 100 mg
Derived from min. dry 1 g
Equiv. caffeine 10 mg

Camellia sinensis (Green Tea) leaf ext. dry conc. stand. 150 mg
Derived from min. dry 2.25 g
Equiv. caffeine 6 mg

Rhodiola rosea (Rhodiola) root ext. dry conc. stand. 72 mg
Derived from min. dry 288 mg
Equiv. rosavin 2.16 mg
Equiv. salidroside 1.44 mg

No added gluten, dairy, lactose, soy, egg, artificial colours or artificial flavours. Suitable for vegetarians and vegans.

Directions

DIRECTIONS FOR USE - ADULT DOSAGE:
Take two capsules daily or as directed by your healthcare practitioner.

STORAGE INSTRUCTIONS

Store below 25°C in a cool, dry place. Do not use if cap seal or inner seal is missing or broken.
